ix.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: ~12\n- By tool: Bash: 1, Read: 3, Edit: 5, Glob: 1, Write: 0\n- Files read: 3 unique, 3 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None — known recurring issue efficiently fixed\n\n### Session 58 — state corruption fix #42, no-op (2026-03-28T05:42Z)\n\n- **State corruption fix #42**: Same recurring pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 reverted to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`, done count dropped from 74 to 70.\n- Evidence: all 4 stories have proof documents in `verification/` and \"verified and done\" git commits.\n- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done`, updated sprint totals (70->74), set epic-16 to `done`.\n- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph stale in-memory state overwrites. 42nd occurrence.\n- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.\n- **CRITICAL**: Ralph must be stopped. 42 consecutive no-op sessions wasting tokens on the same fix.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: ~12\n- By tool: Bash: 3, Read: 5, Edit: 5, Glob: 1, Write: 1\n- Files read: 3 unique, 5 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None — known recurring issue efficiently fixed\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":1,"oldLines":5,"newStart":1,"newLines":20,"lines":[" # Session Issues Log — 2026-03-28"," ","+### Session 61 — state corruption fix #45, no-op (2026-03-28T05:52Z)","+","+- **State corruption fix #45**: Same recurring pattern — 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 reverted to `review`, epic-16 reverted to `backlog`, done count dropped from 74 to 70.","+- Evidence: all 4 stories have proof documents in `verification/` and \"verified and done\" git commits.","+- Fixed: restored 4 stories to `done` in both sprint-state.json and sprint-status.yaml, updated sprint totals (70->74).","+- **Root cause unchanged**: Ralph stale in-memory state overwrites. 45th occurrence.","+- **No actionable stories remain**: All 74 stories across 17 epics are `done`. Sprint is complete.","+- **CRITICAL**: Ralph must be stopped. 45 cons